question: What is the Ultimate Digital Creator workshop about?
answer: The Ultimate Digital Creator workshop features renowned speaker Omar Fahmi and covers topics like Adobe Premiere, Adobe Lightroom, color science, design for attention grabbing, photography, mobile-based videography, and more. It includes hands-on practice, site visits, and one-to-one coaching. Registration opens on May 22, 2023, at 18:00.
